interpretation: The "next track button" card represents the need for forward momentum and progression. This card indicates a desire to move on from the current situation or phase of life and onto the next. It can also signify a need for a change in direction or a fresh start. The "next track button" card urges you to take action towards your goals and not to remain stagnant. It reminds you that there is always a new path to explore and encourages you to embrace new opportunities. This card can also symbolize impatience or restlessness, reminding you to stay focused and not to rush into decisions without proper consideration. Associated keywords include: progress, change, new beginnings, impatience, restlessness, and action.
